      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to deliver exceptional throttle response across the rev range. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. Mechanical highlights include a reinforced rear subframe\u2014addressing a known chassis weak point\u2014and a documented rod bearing service. The suspension maintains its signature MacPherson strut and multi-link setup, providing the neutral handling and tactile feedback synonymous with the M-division. While the car shows honest wear consistent with its 'good' status, the core mechanical components are dialed in for peak performance.",
